body_html:
@AleksandrKrasnoperov I don't have anything more to add on my comment in #11474, which was:

It seems the directory parsing is somehow getting confused and splitting -MNC out of one of the sdk/.../android-MNC/ dirs rather than the appropriate API level. Do you have the indicated APIs from your WORKSPACE file installed? You can check via sdk/tools/android.

Otherwise this might be an issue better asked over at https://github.com/bazelbuild/bazel as this seems more like a Bazel configuration issue than a TF issue.
